Detailed Description

template<typename Val>
template<class T>
class faif::ml::NaiveBayesian< Val >::CategoryData< T >

internal class to connect category and counter or probability

the category collection; connection between category and attribute value. In learining mode used to count train examples, in classifier mode used to calculate probability
